Text: Welcome to Sonys ImageStationmcuilla Welcome and thank you for joining ImageStation Sonys online service for sharing pictures and video clips There are no charges to join to create online albums to store pictures no matter how many to upload and download images or to use many of our services You can easily share picture and video greeting cards created from your images or ours As a thank you for joining ImageStation were giving you free prints each month for months an Introductory Offer of Free Prints redeemable in the ImageStation store There will be a charge for shipping and handling See site for details We want you to enjoy all the benefits that digital photography has to offer and this is an easy way to sample the great quality of ImageStation prints Accept them with our compliments and enjoy the convenience of photoquality prints from your digital pictures To redeem your online coupon just follow these easy steps First you need to upload your pictures to ImageStation Click the upload images link on the Welcome page to do this Next you need to move your images from your Inbox into an album To do this click on the Create Albums tab at the top of the page and follow instructions Once you have created your album click on the Order Prints link at the top of the page Click the Continue button at the bottom of the Prints page See the site for additional details about completing your order Enter your custom Coupon Code in the box on the Shopping Cart page and hit submit Your Coupon Code is ISCT Coupon must be used by November and is only valid for up to ten x prints Thats it When you complete your transaction your discount will be deducted from your final print total Thanks again for joining ImageStation Sonys online service for sharing pictures and video clips Regards Your Friends at ImageStation Quality prints by Ofoto Ranked in print quality in a recent InfoTrends Research Group study ImageStation is a service mark of Sony Electronics Inc Ofoto is a
